#: _guides/kafka-getting-started.adoc
msgid "Solution"
msgstr "解决方案"

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/kafka-getting-started.adoc
msgid ""
"Follow the instructions below to create the applications step by step.\n"
"You can also go directly to the completed example."
msgstr ""

